new_releases.title: New Releases
new_releases.description: Catch up on new releases from the past few years.

441632.title: Bomb City
441632.description: Based on the true story of Brian Deneke, aversion to a group of punks in a conservative Texas town leads to violence and a controversial hate crime.

456664.title: 2036: Origin Unknown
456664.description: A shrewd astronaut works with her ship's artificial intelligence system to uncover the mystery behind an unknown object found on Mars.

460752.title: Easy Money
460752.description: Two brothers begin working the night shift as janitors at a credit recovery office where one decides to swipe more than just his time card.

466545.title: Man From Earth: Holocene
466545.description: A 14,000-year-old teacher, who hides in plain sight, fears for his life and the fate of mankind when four students unearth his powerful secret.

466558.description: A young woman stuck in rural Pennsylvania grapples with sex, drugs and a possible pregnancy that forces her to take a hard look at her life.

475589.title: The Last Boy
475589.description: A boy living in a dying world is sent by his ill mother on a journey to a magical place where the most impossible dreams can come true.

509392.title: Ideal Home
509392.description: A bickering gay couple’s self-indulgent lifestyle is turned upside-down, when the 10-year-old grandson they never knew existed crashes their party.

516221.title: Rockaway
516221.description: A man recalls his tumultuous youth when his big brother and imagination protected him from an abusive father, and his friends who supported him.

526405.title: Balloon
526405.description: Two families build a hot-air balloon to escape East Germany in 1979, but their crash just short of the border leads to an extreme race against time.

527890.title: T-34
527890.description: In 1944, a young lieutenant leads a courageous group of Russian soldiers, trying to escape from German captivity in a half-destroyed, legendary tank.

549471.title: The Lodgers
549471.description: Gothic chiller about twins confined to their haunted home and each other for life until one falls in love with an outsider and challenges the curse.

549527.title: Sweet Country
549527.description: Set in Australia in the 1920s, this is the tale of an Aboriginal farmhand who shoots a white man in self defense, and must run from a ruthless posse.

550589.title: He's Out There
550589.description: While vacationing at their remote lake house, a mother and two daughters fight to fend off a psychopath who’s been planning their abduction for years.

552732.title: Swiped
552732.description: Unexpected consequences ensue when a womanizing college student enlists his nerdy roommate to code the ultimate hookup app.

562130.title: GonJiam: Haunted Asylum
562130.description: The film crew of an online horror series gets far more footage than they bargained for when they shoot an episode in an abandoned asylum.

562775.title: Mermaid Down
562775.description: A mermaid is ripped from the Pacific and brutalized, then ultimately taken to a mental institution by a man who is far from her savior.

568448.title: The Night Eats the World
568448.description: What seems like a nightmare is a horrifying reality for a man who wakes up in Paris as apparently the only survivor of a swarm of killer zombies.

569508.title: Look Away
569508.description: A tormented teen tired of being bullied decides to switch places with her darker alter ego who lives in the mirror, to frightening results.

569765.title: Little Italy
569765.description: Two childhood friends, whose families are both pizzeria owners, become young sweethearts and must protect their romance from petty family rivalries.

570248.title: Girl Lost: A Hollywood Story
570248.description: An honest look at Los Angeles’ sex industry, where young women are pulled into the seedy world, which includes unusual challenges.

570250.title: Mara
570250.description: When a criminal psychologist takes on a mysterious case involving a man strangled to death in bed, she discovers an ancient nightmare demon.

571224.title: Madame
571224.description: An upscale dinner hosted by a couple in Paris goes rogue when their maid poses as royalty and runs off with one of their guests, leading to a chase.

572750.title: The Blackout: Invasion Earth
572750.description: A military crew discovers an outpost of survivors surrounded by corpses, from cars to hospitals, and tries to find out the cause of the mass deaths.

574109.title: Cold Skin
574109.description: A young man’s job as a weather watcher on a remote island becomes monstrous when deadly creatures from the deep start to threaten his watchtower.

574218.title: The Isle
574218.description: A trio of shipwrecked sailors seek shelter on a remote island, but soon discover that the land is haunted by a dark and dangerous secret.

576913.title: Unplanned
576913.description: All Abby Johnson ever wanted to do was help women. As one of the youngest Planned Parenthood clinic directors in the nation, she believed in a woman's right to choose. Until the day she saw something that changed everything.

585776.title: Burning
585776.description: A man agrees to watch an ex-neighbor’s cat while she goes on a trip and becomes suspicious of the man she brings back just before her disappearance.

585846.title: The Gangster, the Cop, the Devil

587321.title: Occupation

595588.title: In the Fade (Dubbed)
595588.description: After a woman’s family is killed in a terrorist attack, she will stop at nothing to make sure the murderers get their fair share of justice.

603411.title: The Collini Case (Subtitled)

603413.title: The Collini Case (Dubbed)
603413.description: Intense legal thriller about a rookie lawyer’s landmark case defending a man with no clear motive who is accused of killing a famous industrialist.

605252.description: After awakening in a disturbing dystopian world filled with memories of comatose patients, an architect must join a group of survivors.

637124.title: Chernobyl 1986 (Subtitled)

but their robberies put their beliefs and bonds under legal scrutiny.
640072.description: A chosen family of small-time thieves take in a child they find on the street, but their robberies put their beliefs and bonds under legal scrutiny.

649977.description: Dave Bautista and Michelle Yeoh throw fists in this story of a defeated criminal who gets drawn closer into a life of crime when he becomes a waiter.

649980.description: The multiple-award-winning action film about a kingdom commander facing betrayal at all angles who has a lookalike shadow who can slay his foes.
